			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="/images/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Another, quicker, way to level your pickpocket(pp) ability is pp something like an orc pawn or a decaying skele until it catches you and starts to attack.  Because the pawn or skele is so much lower it may hit you for 1 or 3 damage every 5 hits.  All you have to do is hit the pp hotkey.  I went from pp level 4 to lvl 45 in one bout.
				</font>
