				Another fun but mildly off way to do it...is when you are at the orc camps...stand near a party that is taking on orcs...claim you are there for the faction...and pick pocket...its mildly satisfying to hear their complaints of no orc belts...or any other items for that matter! Yeah its a bit messed up...but hey...we are rogues aren't we?? 
